cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.RO, cs.HC

The paper deals with computer vision techniques for improving the visual appearance of surgical training phantoms. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and visualization techniques, which makes cs.GR (Computer Graphics) a likely category as well. The use of GANs and deep learning techniques also suggests that cs.MM (Multimedia) could be a relevant category. The paper also involves robotics and human-computer interaction, which makes cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) possible categories.
